Package: pgatouR
Title: R Client for the PGA Tour API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Adam", "Wickwire", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "adam@adamwickwire.com")
Description: Access PGA Tour leaderboards, player stats, scorecards, shot
    tracking data, tee times, FedExCup standings, odds, and more. Wraps
    the PGA Tour GraphQL and REST APIs, returning tidy tibbles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/WalrusQuant/pgatouR
BugReports: https://github.com/WalrusQuant/pgatouR/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite,
    tibble,
    cli
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
